quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"'ina 'anzalna alquran fi laylat alsharaf walfdl, wahi 'ihda layali shahr rmdan"
  97,2,wma 'adrak -ayha alnby- ma laylat alqadr walshrf?
  97,3,"lylt alqadr laylat mbarkt, fadluha khayr min fadl 'alf shahr lays fiha laylat qdr"
  97,4,"ykthr nuzul almalayikat wajibril ealayh alslam fyha, bi'iidhn rabihim min kuli 'amr qdah fi tilk alsnt"
  97,5,"hy 'amn klha, la shrr fiha 'iilaa matlae alfjr"